metadata.name: I'm not a Lone Wolf
metadata.description:
This story about WATARU and his friends.

When he was a kid. He left alone an orphan.
Until one day he got hurt because he stole the food for survive.
He meets two friends (but not human) They saved his life. 
They no where to go like him. 
After that day they live and go on an adventure together.
